Question: You are given the chance to learn how to play a new instrument. Which one would you choose and why?
Answer:
I would pick piano I think because it is an instrument you can play alone without feeling noisy as opposed to drums or any percussions. Also a lot of songs can be easily interpretated on piano. Finally I like piano because it's beautiful and a lot of music we listen to, such as in the movies, use piano. The gesture, when playing, is also kind of romantic. 